{"id":14356,"date":"2024-02-10T17:45:35","date_gmt":"2020-09-10T12:15:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14356"},"modified":"2024-10-26T19:40:27","modified_gmt":"2024-10-26T14:10:27","slug":"white-sofa-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/white-sofa-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"White Sofa Design Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Here&#8217;s a lowdown on our favourite white sofa design ideas to help you pick the best one for your living room!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have always dreamt of designing a cosy living room? Are sceptical about adding white furniture, particularly a white sofa? Well, we say you give it another thought! This blog on beautiful white sofa designs proves how it can make your living room the most inviting space of your house. It further makes it easy for you to decorate as a white sofa is so neutral yet strong that it can blend with almost every decor style.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can be challenging to pick the best white sofa for your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room<\/a> as they all might look the same. But we are here to make it simpler for you. We bring you a list of white sofa design ideas to help you pick the best one!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A White U Shaped Sectional Sofa Set<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A white U-shaped sectional sofa is perfect for a big family or for those who like to entertain a lot! A U-shaped sectional sofa provides a seating space on either side and in the middle forming the shape of the alphabet U as shown in this picture. Sectional sofas are extremely popular and easily available in the market in different types of upholstery and sizes. If a white sectional sofa is a wee bit too much for you, you can add cushions in bright colours, rugs or add white cushions as shown in this image. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173203\/sectional-u-shaped-white-leather-sofa-set.jpg\" alt=\"Sectional u-shaped white leather sofa in this white living room is perfect for a big family.\" class=\"wp-image-14362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173203\/sectional-u-shaped-white-leather-sofa-set.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173203\/sectional-u-shaped-white-leather-sofa-set-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173203\/sectional-u-shaped-white-leather-sofa-set-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173203\/sectional-u-shaped-white-leather-sofa-set-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White Lawson Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Lawson is the classic American sofa style. It is comfortable and smaller compared to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas\/\">sectional sofas<\/a>. A boxed shape Lawson sofa is broad and simple. You can further add loose cushions to enhance the level of comfort. The arms of a lawson sofa aren\u2019t necessarily rolled either making it easier to clean. A white lawson sofa design is an excellent pick if you have a tiny knit family. Also, there are several materials, textures and patterns to choose from, making it a perfect choice for the new age living rooms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172919\/lawson-white-leather-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Lawson white sofa in living room is an excellent pick if you have a tiny knit family.\" class=\"wp-image-14359\" style=\"width:840px;height:504px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172919\/lawson-white-leather-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172919\/lawson-white-leather-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172919\/lawson-white-leather-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172919\/lawson-white-leather-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Interior designs to brighten your living room\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/26185421\/interior-designs-brighten-living-room.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White L-Shaped Sectional Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you think that a sectional sofa is too big to fit in a small living room you might want to think again. An <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/l-shaped-sectional-sofa\/\">L-shaped sectional sofa<\/a> is versatile to fit into almost every size of the living room. We recommend you choose a three-seater L-shaped sofa and place it in the corner of your living room. This arrangement will let you fully utilise the confined floor space and offer ample seating space and free space to move around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173255\/sectional-white-l-shaped-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"An white l-shaped sofa in an all-white living room - perfect for minimalist interior design\" class=\"wp-image-14363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173255\/sectional-white-l-shaped-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173255\/sectional-white-l-shaped-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173255\/sectional-white-l-shaped-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173255\/sectional-white-l-shaped-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White Mid-Century Modern Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A white mid-century sofa can instantly make your small living room look spacious. This sofa design is famous for its high elevated seating with a classy silhouette and sleek lines. It as the three seats are removable and the elevated structure leaves a gap between the floor and sofa. These sofas are available in easily available in different textures and materials and can be easily blended in every style and size of the living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173111\/mid-century-modern-white-fabric-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"The mid-century modern white sofa is super easy to clean and can easily blend in every style and size of the living room.\" class=\"wp-image-14361\" style=\"width:840px;height:504px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173111\/mid-century-modern-white-fabric-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173111\/mid-century-modern-white-fabric-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173111\/mid-century-modern-white-fabric-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173111\/mid-century-modern-white-fabric-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/mid-century-modern-sofa-design\/\">Mid-Century Modern Sofa Design<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White Chesterfield Sofa Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The name alone, Chesterfield sofa, carries with it an air of style and royalty. The easiest way to spot a chesterfield sofa is to look for deep tufting of buttons on the back. The hunky Chesterfield sofa makes a powerful statement in any living room. High arms and a deep seat characterise it. Also, the wraparound design gives you a cosy seat that is roomy enough for your entire family to pile on. However, you must remember that its generous scale requires a room with some size to maintain balance. If you are convinced with the idea of having a white chesterfield sofa in your living room, we recommend you take it one level higher and pick the one with the velvet upholstery.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172825\/chesterfield-white-sofa-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Chesterfield white leather sofa set design gives a cosy seat that is roomy enough for the entire family to pile on.\" class=\"wp-image-14358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172825\/chesterfield-white-sofa-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172825\/chesterfield-white-sofa-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172825\/chesterfield-white-sofa-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10172825\/chesterfield-white-sofa-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White Low-Height Modern Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bring home the farmhouse vibes to your living room with a low-height sofa design. This sofa design is exceptionally comfortable and cosy perfect for snuggling with your family and binge-watch your favourite shows together. Throw in a quilt and some cushions to make this make it even more comfortable as shown in the image. It would be great if you have a wood-panelled floor but if you don&#8217;t, add a rug in earthy tones to make this stunning sofa stand out!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173012\/low-height-modern-white-sofa-set.jpg\" alt=\"Low-height modern white sofa on wooden floor in a living room\" class=\"wp-image-14360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173012\/low-height-modern-white-sofa-set.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173012\/low-height-modern-white-sofa-set-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173012\/low-height-modern-white-sofa-set-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10173012\/low-height-modern-white-sofa-set-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And it&#8217;s a wrap for today! We hope that these white sofa design ideas help you pick the right one for your living room!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Happy Decorating!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/different-sofa-styles-for-your-home\/\">Different Sofa Styles For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/15-sofa-designs-for-modern-living-room\/\">15 Sofa Designs For Modern Living Room<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p clas